{"article_id":"H7mtSXMLW9n68Pup","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FORT BRAGG , N.C.","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"U.S. Army Sergeant Bowe Bergdahl on Friday was spared prison","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"for endangering his comrades in arms","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"when he deserted in Afghanistan in 2009 ,","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"a sentence","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"swiftly condemned by President Donald Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"who","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"while seeking election","depth":13},{"id":9,"text":"had called for his execution .","depth":13},{"id":10,"text":"\" The decision on Sergeant Bergdahl is a complete and total disgrace to our Country and to our Military , \"","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Trump posted on Twitter from Air Force One","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"as he flew to Asia at the start of a lengthy tour of the region .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"A military judge recommended","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that Bergdahl should be dishonorably discharged from the service ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"demoted to private","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"and forfeit $ 10,000 in pay .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Army Colonel Jeffery Nance took less than a minute","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"to render his decision","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"and made no other comment .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Bergdahl was captured eight years ago by the Taliban","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"after walking off his combat outpost .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"He endured torture and malnutrition","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"while held prisoner by the insurgent group for nearly five years .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"His case sparked a national debate","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"over whether he was a victim or a villain .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The soldier ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"who had pleaded guilty to desertion and misbehavior before the enemy ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"faced a maximum term of life in prison .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Late Friday morning , the 31-year-old Hailey , Idaho , native trembled","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"as he waited to hear his punishment in a courtroom in Fort Bragg , North Carolina .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Defense lawyers ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"who had urged Nance to show leniency ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"after sentencing","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"that Bergdahl was relieved and eager to move on ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"though they would not discuss his plans .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Bergdahl has remained on active duty at Fort Sam Houston in San Antonio , Texas .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"\" This has been a terrible ordeal , \"","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"said one of his lawyers , Eugene Fidell .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Neither Bergdahl nor prosecutors ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"who had sought a 14-year prison term ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"commented .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Soldiers","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"who testified about the hardships and injuries","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"suffered in the hunt for Bergdahl","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"after he walked off his post in Paktika province in June 2009","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"without permission","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"they were disappointed by the sentence .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"\" It ' s definitely a slap in the face , \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"former Army Specialist Jonathan Morita said in a phone interview .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Morita ' s right hand was mangled by a rocket-propelled grenade during a July 2009 raid","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"seeking intelligence on Bergdahl ' s whereabouts .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Along with criticism over the years from U.S. political leaders and fellow soldiers over the dangerous searches","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"prompted by Bergdahl ' s actions ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"the conditions of his release sparked controversy .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"U.S. Army Sergeant Bowe Bergdahl","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"( R )","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"arrives at the courthouse for the eighth day of sentencing proceedings in his court martial at Fort Bragg , North Carolina , U.S. , November 3 , 2017 .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"/Jonathan Drake","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"In May 2014 , Bergdahl was handed over to U.S. special operations troops in Afghanistan in exchange for five Taliban detainees ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"who were released from the Guantanamo Bay prison","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and flown to Qatar .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Last year , as a Republican presidential candidate , Trump called Bergdahl \" a no-good traitor","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"who should have been executed . \"","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Responding to a defense motion on Trump ' s comments ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Colonel Nance ruled","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"they had not influenced him","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"nor affected Bergdahl ' s chances of a fair sentence .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"However , the judge said","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"he would consider them a mitigating factor .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Defense attorney Fidell said on Friday","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that Americans should be offended by Trump ' s behavior .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" President Trump ' s unprincipled effort","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"to stoke a lynch-mob atmosphere","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"while seeking our nation ' s highest office","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"has cast a dark cloud over the case , \"","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"A dishonorable discharge ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"issued for the most serious offenses ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"cuts off all military and veterans benefits ,","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"including healthcare from the Department of Veterans Affairs .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"That could pose difficulties for Bergdahl ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"who ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"according to testimony ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"suffered significant nerve damage while a Taliban prisoner","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and has several mental health conditions .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"His punishment must be approved by the commanding general of the U.S. Army Forces Command","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and then will automatically be reviewed on appeal .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"The discharge will not take effect","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"until an appellate court affirms Bergdahl ' s conviction and sentence .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Defense lawyers said","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"he was a young , hardworking soldier","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"who did not understand the full consequences of his actions","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"when he left","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"to report what he said","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"were problems in his unit .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Bergdahl apologized in court this week for the pain","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"he caused fellow service members","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"and admitted","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"he had made \" a horrible mistake . \"","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"But prosecutors said","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Bergdahl knew","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"he would trigger alarm in the war zone .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"They acknowledged","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"he suffered during his years as a Taliban prisoner ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"but argued","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"it resulted from his choices","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"and did not diminish the harm","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"he caused others .","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"Retired Army Lieutenant Colonel Jeffrey Addicott said","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"he was surprised by the judge ' s decision .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"\" You had several members of our military","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"who have been maimed for the rest of their life","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"because of what Bergdahl did ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"so he should have received jail time , in my opinion , \"","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"said Addicott , now a law professor at St. Mary ' s University in San Antonio , Texas .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":235,"left":0,"right":234,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":234,"left":1,"right":233,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":233,"left":172,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":158,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":141,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":135,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":128,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":125,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":120,"right":124,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":2,"right":119,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":5,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":7,"right":121,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":121,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":10,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":131,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":13,"right":130,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":1